{"word":"G1483 - ἐθνικῶς - ethnikōs - eth-nee-koce' - After the manner of Gentiles","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐθνικῶς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ethnikōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">eth-nee-koce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">After the manner of Gentiles</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"புறஜாதியார் முறைமையாக - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"like the Gentiles"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G1482 - ἐθνικός - ethnikós - eth-nee-kos'/1482\">G1482</a>; <i>as a Gentile:</i> - after the manner of Gentiles.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1482/1482\">G1482</a>, <a href=\"#/G1483/1483\">G1483</a>, <a href=\"#/G1484/1484\">G1484</a>"}]}